name: Downlogram
overview: Downlogram is a search engine for free files and downloads. The company’s vision is to provide a free natural language approach to file and downloads search. As most of today’s software titles provide little to no information about the actual utility of different software solutions, Downlogram’s approach is to allow the user to search for phrases that express her or his needs, such as “convert zip to rar files” or “edit image files”. All the software in the search repository are either open source or free under various licenses. Currently, Downlogram is PC-focused, but the next version will feature iOS and Android sections as well.
